ive]]\n| [[Arthur Balfour]]{{ref label|2|2|2}}\n| [[File:Picture of Arthur Balfour.jpg|60px]]\n| '''[[Robert Gascoyne-Cecil, 3rd Marquess of Salisbury|The Marquess of Salisbury]]'''{{ref label|3|3|3}}\n| [[File:Robert cecil.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| June 1895\n|style=\"background-color: {{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" rowspan=\"5\"|\n|rowspan=\"5\"| [[Liberal Party (UK)|Liberal]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[William Harcourt (politician)|Sir William Harcourt]]{{ref label|C|C|C}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[File:Sir William Harcourt.jpg|60px]]\n| '''[[Archibald Primrose, 5th Earl of Rosebery|The Earl of Rosebery]]'''{{ref label|1|1|1}}{{ref label|D|D|D}}\n| [[File:The Earl of Rosebery.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| January 1897\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[John Wodehouse, 1st Earl of Kimberley|The Earl of Kimberley]]{{ref label|\u2020|\u2020|\u2020}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[File:1st Earl of Kimberley 1897.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| 6 February 1899\n|rowspan=\"3\"| '''[[Henry Campbell-Bannerman|Sir Henry Campbell-Bannerman]]'''{{ref label|2|2|2}}\n|rowspan=\"3\"| [[File:Picture of Henry Campbell-Bannerman.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| 1902\n| [[John Spencer, 5th Earl Spencer|The Earl Spencer]]\n| [[File:Picture of John Spencer, 5th Earl Spencer.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| 1905\n| [[George Robinson, 1st Marquess of Ripon|The Marquess of Ripon]]\n| [[File:George Robinson 1st Marquess of Ripon.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| 5 December 1905\n|style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" rowspan=\"4\"| \n|rowspan=\"4\"| [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]]\n| '''[[Arthur Balfour]]'''{{ref label|1|1|1}}{{ref label|E|E|E}}\n| [[File:Picture of Arthur Balfour.jpg|60px]]\n|rowspan=\"4\"| [[Henry Petty-Fitzmaurice, 5th Marquess of Lansdowne|The Marquess of Lansdowne]]<br />([[Liberal Unionist Party]] until 1912)\n|rowspan=\"4\"| [[File:Marquess of Lansdowne crop.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| 1906\n| ''[[Joseph Chamberlain]]''<br />([[Liberal Unionist Party]])\n| [[File:Picture of Joseph Chamberlain.jpg|60px]]\n|-\n| 1906\n| '''[[Arthur Balfour]]'''{{ref lab